&lt;p&gt;Across the SaaS (Software as a Service) industry, the role of Customer Success is being developed; yet because it’s so new, people usually do not understand what it is. In essence, it’s all about customer service, support and satisfaction. Gone are the days of a simple sale. A new era has begun where a company must nurture its customers to drive renewals and up-sell revenue through a long-term, engineered strategy; thus, the development of “Customer Success.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a Customer Success Coach, this team member will support the Director of Customer Success in the active management of the eVisit customer experience, engagement and satisfaction.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;JOB RESPONSIBILITIES:&lt;/h3&gt;
