  &lt;li&gt;Administer customer product training to ensure strong adoption, usage and ongoing engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Play a leading role in empowering and advising customers on optimal approaches to implementation and patient adoption challenges based on intimate understanding of product, industry and customer needs.&lt;/li&gt;
