  &lt;li&gt;Oversee periodic customer success reviews to help ensure operational effectiveness and customer satisfaction and drive continuous improvement of platform through careful consideration of customer feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Develop materials for customers to assist in driving eVisit’s customers’ best possible product use and satisfaction, including tutorial videos, job aids, knowledge-based articles and new feature/product releases emails.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Support in efforts to increase renewal rates, reduce churn and expand revenue through cross-sell and up-sell opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
